After many long months, we can finally share the news! Being a “police wife” was never in my plans for the future. On October 23rd that changes, as Hunter starts his first day. My husband, my best friend….
The past year hasn’t been easy for us. However, I believe if it wasn’t for the many doors closing, you wouldn’t be where you are now. Your hard work, dedication, focus and commitment has landed you right here. I am so proud of you! ❤️🫶✨ Keep up the hard work and you will do amazing things! 

Psalms 130:5 NIV
